\n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n                                                        \n                                \n                                \n                                                \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n                                                        \n                                \n                                \n                                                \n            \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                \n    \n    \n        \n    \n\n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n            \n    \n    \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n            \n    \n    \n        \n                \n                    \n                        \n                                    \u003cdiv id=\"article-body\" itemprop=\"articleBody\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIf you\u0026#39;re looking to reduce the cost of your wireless plan, going with \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/best-prepaid-phone-plans/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ea prepaid carrier\u003c/a\u003e might be the way to go. Not only will you get excellent wireless coverage, but brands often feature impressive discounts for those looking to switch.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n    \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"a6ef-4f11-a156e590b418\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/total-wireless-review/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/total-wireless-review-download-town-4.jpeg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/total-wireless-review-download-town-4.jpeg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/total-wireless-review-download-town-4.jpeg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/total-wireless-review-download-town-4.jpeg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/total-wireless-review-download-town-4.jpeg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/total-wireless-review-download-town-4.jpeg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/total-wireless-review-download-town-4.jpeg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/total-wireless-review-download-town-4.jpeg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/total-wireless-review-download-town-4.jpeg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"4032\" height=\"2268\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"Total Wireless speed test in town square, 24.89Mbps down shown with 5G UW signal\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/total-wireless-review-download-town-4.jpeg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/01/total-wireless-review-download-town-4.jpeg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWith that said, \u003ca href=\"https://totalwireless.sjv.io/c/2233363/2919901/15774?subId1=news\u0026amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.totalwireless.com%2Fkyop\u0026amp;partnerpropertyid=3672917\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eTotal Wireless is making a huge push right now\u003c/a\u003e, offering some exciting promotions that look to lure Cricket and Metro customers to their brand. The wireless carrier is now taking 50% off its usual pricing for those that are looking to switch, which means plans now start at just $20.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"a-tempting-offer-for-those-looking-to-switch\"\u003e\n                        A tempting offer for those looking to switch\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n    \n    \n    \n\n\u003cp\u003eSo if the promotion sounds tempting, there are a few things you need to know before jumping in. First is that you need to currently be a customer on Metro or Cricket that\u0026#39;s looking to switch carriers. You\u0026#39;ll also need an unlocked device, so that you can use the service once it\u0026#39;s activated.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThe fine print also states that you need to switch from a comparable unlimited plan in order to take advantage, which means, if you\u0026#39;re on a $30 plan on Cricket, then you\u0026#39;ll need to get something similar from Total Wireless. If you\u0026#39;re unsure about this point, we recommend speaking to someone from the brand in order to get things clarified before making the change.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eFor the most part, though, since Total Wireless is a competitor, there are plans that are similar to those being offered by Cricket and Metro. On the Base plan, you\u0026#39;ll get unlimited talk, text, and data for just $20 per month, and the Total 5G plan will offer the same, with just faster data, along with 15GB of hotspot data for $25 per month.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eThose looking to get the most out of their plan will want to opt for the Total 5G+ plan that cost $30 per month, which adds unlimited hotspot access. The plans look pretty good thanks to the impressive 50% discount. All the plans will reward subscribers for sticking around for 12 months with a $200 credit that can be used to purchase a new handset.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eFor the most part, not a bad deal considering that you\u0026#39;re score 50% off. Perhaps the cherry on top here is that Total Wireless is offering a five-year price lock on all its plans, which should provide some peace of mind for anyone that\u0026#39;s looking to switch.\u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                                \n        \n                            \n         